peed":22,"fuelCapacity":2600,"cabinLayout":[{"label":"Master Cabin","value":"1"},{"label":"VIP Cabin","value":"1"},{"label":"Twin Cabin","value":"1"}],"cabins":3,"bathrooms":3,"length":16.3,"beam":4.7,"draft":0,"engines":"2 X 660 hp CAT","amenities":[{"label":"Air Conditioning"},{"label":"Fridge"},{"label":"Freezer"},{"label":"Cooker/Stove"},{"label":"Oven"},{"label":"Coffee Machine"},{"label":"Microwave"},{"label":"Water Maker"},{"label":"Ice Maker"},{"label":"Dishwasher"},{"label":"Washing Machine"},{"label":"Heating System"},{"label":"Outside Shower"},{"label":"Sun Pads"},{"label":"GPS Plotter"},{"label":"Solar Panels"},{"label":"Teak deck (whole deck, not only the cockpit)"},{"label":"Electric winches"},{"label":"Radar"},{"label":"Inverter"},{"label":"Autopilot"},{"label":"Bimini"},{"label":"Bow thruster"},{"label":"Bathing platform"},{"label":"Generator"}],"toys":[{"label":"Jetski","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Seabob","quantity":"1"},{"label":"SUP","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Water Ski","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Wake board","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Tubes","quantity":"1"}],"entertainment":["Outside deck speakers","Radio CD / MP3 player / Audio system","Inside speakers","Flat screen TV"],"tenders":["High Field 3.40m - 40HP"]},"crew":[{"name":"Christos Moraitis","role":"Captain","bio":"Experienced yacht captain with over 14 years at sea, specializing in both private and charter operations on motor and sailing yachts up to 25 meters. Known for being reliable, calm under pressure, and maintaining high standards of safety, comfort, and service onboard. Fully trained in all necessary maritime procedures, including safety drills and offshore navigation.\nExtensive knowledge of the Greek islands and Mediterranean cruising areas, with the ability to plan smooth, enjoyable itineraries tailored to every journey. Focused on creating a safe, relaxed, and memorable experience, while sharing hidden beaches, beautiful bays, and local highlights. Skilled at adapting plans to the conditions at sea and the preferences of guests, ensuring a seamless and enjoyable trip.\nProfessional, discreet, and approachable, with a natural ability to work with different personalities and make everyone feel comfortable. Dedicated to providing a high-quality charter experience that combines safety, comfort, and the pleasure of exploring the sea."},{"name":"Alexia Michailidi","role":"Captain","bio":"Friendly and professional hostess with a passion for making guests feel welcome and creating enjoyable experiences onboard. Skilled at noticing details, staying organized, and helping the crew keep everything running smoothly.\nOutgoing, approachable, and positive, always ready to assist with guest needs, serve meals and drinks, and maintain a clean and comfortable environment. Eager to learn new skills and gain experience in all aspects of life on board.\nFamiliar with the Greek islands and Mediterranean destinations, able to offer local tips, suggest activities, and add thoughtful touches to enhance the guest experience.\nReliable, discreet, and committed, with a strong work ethic and a genuine desire to make every trip safe, relaxing, and memorable. \nEnjoys working as part of a team and building good relationships with crew and guests alike."},{"name":"Stergios Anagnostou","role":"Captain","bio":"Enthusiastic and energetic deckhand, always ready to help and keen to learn. Young and motivated, with a positive attitude and lots of energy, happy to take on any task to support the crew and keep things running smoothly onboard.\nFriendly, reliable, and hardworking, comfortable helping with deck work, cleaning, and water activities. Quick to learn and easy to work with, excited to gain experience and improve skills at sea. Enjoys life on board and is committed to making every trip safe, fun, and memorable for everyone.\nEager to grow as a crew member, open to guidance, and ready to take on new challenges while learning all aspects of working on a yacht."}],"pricing":{"d